Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.75,0:00:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming in, Tsunade.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.08,0:00:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiraiya? Did you learn anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.05,0:00:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I discovered the whereabouts\Nof the Akatsuki leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.74,0:00:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Is that true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.87,0:00:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me more!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.28,0:00:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll use that information\Nto plan a surprise attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.04,0:00:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be hasty, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.55,0:00:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't like plotting\Na sequel to your novel!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.17,0:00:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have the time to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.79,0:00:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Haste makes waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.12,0:00:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially with the stakes\Nthis high...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.77,0:00:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, why don't we grab a drink together?\N Just you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.39,0:00:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you everything there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.43,0:00:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool! I am the Hokage!\N And you're asking me to go drinking in broad daylight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.24,0:00:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you no shame when\Nour ninja are on duty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.57,0:00:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.06,0:00:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You really ought to take your own words\Na bit more to heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.24,0:01:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Drinking sake straight out\Nof the bottle...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.80,0:01:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, you {\i1}are{\i0} the Hokage, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:39.80,Title,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(812.813,577.5)}Twilight\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.52,0:02:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl's late...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,How long does it take to\Npick up supplies...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish it would get dark soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.19,0:02:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After Jugo and Suigetsu turn in,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll make my move on Sasuke\N{\i1}while he sleeps!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:02:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Kiba?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.93,0:03:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm concentrating, trying to\Nsingle out Sasuke's faint scent!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.14,0:03:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So shut up! You're distracting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no mistake...\N{\i1}They're steadily approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One...two...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.64,0:03:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Their chakra is strong too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.09,0:03:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There're quite a few.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.58,0:03:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I sense non-human chakra too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.93,0:03:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dogs?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.44,0:03:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are they tracking our scent?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it Akatsuki?\N{\i1}Or maybe the Hidden Leaf?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.09,0:03:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Jugo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.76,0:03:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go check on Karin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:04:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.52,0:04:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up, Sasuke! \NWe're going to have company! What do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.38,0:04:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sasuke just waking up...is also nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.13,0:04:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We escape... Get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.21,0:04:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Jugo, mark every Akatsuki hideout\Nthat we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're okay now, Sasuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I've been healing a lot faster\Nsince I absorbed Orochimaru's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.35,0:04:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So this is the Power of the White Snake...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it's Akatsuki or the Hidden Leaf,\N they might have information on Itachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So why don't we ambush them, Sasuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.45,0:04:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,From what you reported about the number\N of people, it's most likely the Hidden Leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Akatsuki always work\Nin two-man cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means an ambush\Nwould be a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. Forget the Hidden Leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.39,0:05:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what'll we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi is our only priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we locate him, worse comes to worst,\N you three must stop the Hidden Leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, team "Hebi" will use\Nthe information gathered by Jugo
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.78,0:05:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and check out Akatsuki hideouts\None by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.65,0:05:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me out for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.26,0:05:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,With that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.63,0:05:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you gather as many birds\Nas you can?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.57,0:05:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you plan on doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Sasuke's old outfit.\N It's soaked with his sweat and smell, so we'll use this to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.35,0:05:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you have an outfit\Nthat Sasuke threw away?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...! Th-That...\NThat's not important...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hate to do this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:06:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensory-Type Ninja have different\N specialties depending on their village.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.81,0:06:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hidden Leaf often use ninja hounds.\N So we'll use that to our advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Kiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.05,0:06:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot! Sasuke is starting to move!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry!\NSasuke is going after Itachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.60,0:06:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it, something's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.81,0:06:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke's scent is dispersing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.30,0:06:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only that,\Nit's scattering in all directions!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.60,0:06:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He's on to us.\NTaking strategic action.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.98,0:06:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,On to us? But how?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.53,0:06:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what kind of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.67,0:06:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm guessing he has\Na skilled Sensory-Type Ninja on his side.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.55,0:06:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The distance is too great,\N so I can't guide you through the wireless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one\Nwho can pursue him...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's one scent. What'll we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.55,0:06:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find him if I have to search\Nevery blade of grass!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,With whatever means necessary!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Multiple Shadow Clone Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's up ahead...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.35,0:07:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys wait until I give the order.\NI'll go and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who's that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.08,0:07:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sharingan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.47,0:07:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sasuke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Th-That's--!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.85,0:07:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Itachi...Uchiha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on out... Naruto Uzumaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You've come to capture me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.26,0:08:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No...I didn't.\NI just came to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I'd ever trust you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.86,0:08:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When up against the Sharingan,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.20,0:08:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}if it's one on one, always run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.74,0:08:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If it's two against one,\N{\i1}get his back...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But in his case...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.87,0:08:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even while making a seal, {\i1}he can put his target\N under a genjutsu {\i1}using only finger movements...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.18,0:08:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that you're alone.\NSo why don't you run?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hah! My numbers can go from\None to a thousand!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.53,0:08:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I can't run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.34,0:08:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If I capture you, I get to see Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.15,0:09:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so attached to my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a Rogue Ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.49,0:09:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because unlike you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I think of him as a brother\Nmore than you ever would.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're already under my genjutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.65,0:09:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.71,0:09:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.53,0:09:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to talk to you\Nfor a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.11,0:09:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This Akatsuki leader is in\Nthe Hidden Rain Village, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But that place conducts thorough checks\Nof anyone entering and exiting their territory,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.10,0:10:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and they track\Nhow long visitors stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.21,0:10:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Just preparing for the Chunin Exams is difficult each\N time because the village is so closed off to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't seem like a place where\Nthe Akatsuki leader can move about freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.63,0:10:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,However...because security is so strict,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,they're able to keep other nations\Nfrom learning about their internal affairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and hence, keep a lid on any shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Shame?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that land has seen much internal strife,\N and the village itself has been split into two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.95,0:10:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Word has it that the leader of one side\Nis also the leader of Akatsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.38,0:10:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That land is surrounded by the three\N great nations of Earth, Wind and Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.63,0:10:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And from ages past, it has been\N the battleground of their conflicts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.26,0:10:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result, there has never been domestic stability\N and the number of refugees is continually on the rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:11:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why I will infiltrate and verify\N the information we have gathered.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.41,0:11:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we can plan strategy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.85,0:11:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too dangerous to go alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.83,0:11:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I am one of the Legendary Sannin\Nof the Leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what that means as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.88,0:11:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,that you always get\Nthe short end of the stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.75,0:11:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.04,0:11:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying, you were\Nsupposed to be Hokage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.65,0:11:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The Third Hokage always wanted you\Nto be the next to--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.75,0:11:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I was never cut out for\Nthat sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.03,0:11:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Being on my own suits me too well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You regretted not being able\Nto stop Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.81,0:11:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So all that time, you were tracking\N his movements alone, isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I no longer need to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.57,0:11:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That means I get to release\Nthe sequel to my novel sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.24,0:12:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Fact is stranger than fiction, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.75,0:12:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would have imagined that\NOrochimaru would die...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember how the three of us would\Ngo up against Old Man Third and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The flat-chested Tsunade has\Nbecome the big-bosomed Hokage!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.66,0:12:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Times are changing by the second.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You were beautiful back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.16,0:12:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and now, you're a\Nfifty-something old granny.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.06,0:12:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It pains me to see how all the memories\Nof your lost friends and loved ones
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,are stored inside\Nthat big breast of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.65,0:12:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And you know, the number\Nwill continue to grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I shouldn't\Nwallow in sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.25,0:12:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,My duty is to be a model for the\N next generation and to help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.85,0:12:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,For that, I'd happily give my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.26,0:13:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what makes us old folks cool, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.85,0:13:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you after me?\NThen this is your...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.38,0:13:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an important task to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shadow Clone...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.84,0:13:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.72,0:13:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! This one's a bust too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.41,0:13:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Naruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.24,0:13:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.95,0:13:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I just tripped.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.78,0:14:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind that.\NKiba, track the next scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.41,0:14:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Your drinking habits are\Nworse than mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.39,0:14:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to stop and rest somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.07,0:14:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's late. We have to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- Okay!\N- Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.80,0:14:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Akatsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The leader is capable of organizing\Na group so powerful...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.60,0:14:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows how strong he may be?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.73,0:14:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be walking right into\Nthe enemy's territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.41,0:14:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then... I should set out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.63,0:14:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If I lost you too... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.12,0:14:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll cry for me?\NThat'll make me happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.99,0:14:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But I doubt that it'll be\Nlike the time Dan died.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.17,0:14:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.84,0:15:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about making a bet with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet that I will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.43,0:15:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, you always lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I make it back alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.56,0:15:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Joking! I'm just joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.13,0:15:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I'm grateful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Rejection makes a man stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.18,0:15:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, you can't call yourself a real\N man unless you can laugh off stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Better yet, make a joke out it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So a man's duty is to be strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.95,0:15:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.49,0:15:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides... men aren't the only ones\Nwho seek happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.94,0:16:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Humph... Stop trying to act so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Without a woman,\Nyou guys can't be rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything happens,\Ncontact me through your toad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.99,0:16:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll rush over myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.84,0:16:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No need for that.\NYou must not leave here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.56,0:16:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The village relies on you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.09,0:16:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There are other candidates\Nfor Hokage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There can be no stability\Nif the Hokage keeps changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.19,0:16:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, you are the only one\Nwho can be Hokage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.44,0:16:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There's Kakashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.79,0:16:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And eventually, there's also Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.43,0:17:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really sold on Naruto, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.88,0:17:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Although, I can understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.49,0:17:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Your kid brother Nawaki...\NYour sweetheart Dan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- It's my dream to become Hokage.\N{\i1}- It's my dream to become Hokage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And Naruto too...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.48,0:17:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you could say\Nthey chased the same dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.96,0:17:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, Kakashi can step in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.12,0:17:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But Naruto still has a long way to go,\Neven though you gave him your necklace.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You have high hopes\Nfor him too...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.48,0:17:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You taught him the Rasengan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.75,0:17:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh that... Well, call it nostalgia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.91,0:17:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It reminded me of the days\Nwhen I taught Minato.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Minato Namikaze...\NTrue, Naruto does resemble him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Minato was a genius that appears\Nonly once in a generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.52,0:18:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There won't be another like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He was kind-hearted,\Nbut had nerves of steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.98,0:18:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He rose to become\Nthe Fourth Hokage so swiftly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.03,0:18:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never been a parent, so I don't know\Nmuch about these things...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.96,0:18:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but if he had been my son,\NI think I'd have been awfully proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it...\NNaruto might not resemble him, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than a son you boast about,\N he'd be the problem child, always up to mischief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.83,0:18:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto is more like his mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.39,0:18:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't she a former kunoichi\Nfrom the Land of Eddies...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.80,0:18:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... His personality and ninjutsu style\Nis just like Kushina Uzumaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.26,0:18:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...that's her name!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.39,0:18:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That talkative, red-haired rascal...\NShe was such a tomboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.83,0:18:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Kushina grew up to be a beauty,\Nbut Naruto looks like his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.44,0:18:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see Naruto's father in him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.14,0:19:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,To me, it feels as though\NI'm looking at my grandson.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.16,0:19:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It is being passed on...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the will of the Leaf,\Nfrom the past to the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.14,0:19:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll be off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.11,0:19:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I had one last warning for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.76,0:19:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Beware of the Foundation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.81,0:19:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Good then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.92,0:19:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell.
